@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Web Application</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="text-center" style="padding-top: 40px;">
        <img src="~/Images/Hero2.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="ePegboard in action" />

        <div style="padding: 30px 15px;">
            <h2 style="color: darkgreen; font-weight: bold;">Run Smarter, Fairer Badminton Club Nights</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                ePegboard replaces traditional pegboards with AI-powered court pairings — reduce wait time, rotate players fairly, and create more competitive games.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3" asp-area="" asp-page="/Download">Download Free Trial For Windows</a>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #333; font-weight: 500;">
                Already powering club nights throughout Milton Keynes — and expanding across the UK.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <section class="text-center" style="padding: 40px 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 style="font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">Your Club Night, Perfectly Run</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 15px;">
                ePegboard is smart, offline-ready software designed to run your badminton club nights with precision. It auto-generates balanced games using player ratings, waiting times, and rotation history — while giving organizers full control when needed.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
                From intelligent court usage and performance tracking to flexible game assignment and audio announcements, ePegboard handles the details so you can focus on great sessions. It's touchscreen-friendly, export-ready, and trusted by real clubs.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <div class="container text-center" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <img src="~/Images/pegboard-vs-epegboard2.png"
                 alt="Traditional pegboard vs. ePegboard software"
                 class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />

            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #555; margin-top: 15px;">
                From manual pegboards to intelligent court assignment — ePegboard brings your club nights into the 21st century.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 40px;">How Club Nights Work with ePegboard</h3>

            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="~/Images/add_player_photos.jpg" alt="Player sign-in screen" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>1. Add Players</h5>
                    <p>Quickly register players as they arrive — including drop-ins and last-minute changes. Just start typing their name or click from the photo gallery.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                    <img src="~/Images/Next_game_sample.jpg" alt="Court assignment screen" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <h5>2. Let ePegboard Build the Games</h5>
                    <p>Use smart auto-pairing based on rest time, past matchups, and player level — or let the first-in-line picker choose, with assistive suggestions from the system.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="~/Images/full_court.jpg" alt="Game announcement screen" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>3. Announce and Play</h5>
                    <p>Display game assignments clearly on-screen — or announce them via audio if you choose. Everyone knows where to go, and court time stays fully used.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                    <img src="~/Images/leaderboard-sample.png" alt="Live leaderboard screenshot" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <h5>4. See Your Stats in Real Time</h5>
                    <p>Players track win percentage, rating changes, and full match history during the session. The leaderboard keeps everyone engaged — especially in competitive clubs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">Designed for Everyone on Court</h3>
            <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                Don’t just assign courts – run the kind of sessions players come back for.
            </p>

            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-5 mb-4">
                    <h5>🎾 For Players</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                        <li>✅ Less waiting</li>
                        <li>✅ More balanced games</li>
                        <li>✅ Smarter rotation</li>
                        <li>✅ Competitive edge</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5 mb-4">
                    <h5>📋 For Club Night Organizers</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                        <li>✅ Happy players</li>
                        <li>✅ More renewals & new members</li>
                        <li>✅ Fairer sessions</li>
                        <li>✅ Helps with league pairing decisions</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 40px;">Powerful Features That Make Club Nights Run Smoothly</h3>

            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>🎯 Smart Game Recommendations</h5>
                    <p>Auto-pairing based on ratings, wait time, and fairness ensures great games for everyone — every round.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>📊 Player Stats & Insights</h5>
                    <p>Track performance, predict outcomes, and view historic data to help with league pairings and club decisions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>📋 Flexible Game Control</h5>
                    <p>Admins can manually override matchups when needed — balancing tradition with smart automation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>🔊 Automated Announcements</h5>
                    <p>Connect to a speaker system and use your device’s audio to announce upcoming games and players — no more shouting across the courts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>📁 Easy Data Exports</h5>
                    <p>Export attendance, match history, and payments in common formats for easy club reporting and tracking.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>💻 Offline, Affordable & Intuitive</h5>
                    <p>Designed for offline use with a touchscreen-friendly interface. No subscriptions, just one smart solution.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>